events.title: DPN – CEC: School Rating System for Detroit Community Meeting
events.description:
Please join the Community Education Commission to learn more about the School Rating System for Detroit. Hosted by the Detroit Parent Network where parents are equipped and empowered as champions for their children and change! Sponsored by the Community Education Commission (CEC), comprised of 11 volunteer members committed to high quality schools for all Detroit children. For more information on the CEC, call 313 224-1222.

TO RSVP call DPN at 313-832-0617 – space is limited.
